{
  "name": "RPlog_An_Abyssal_Union",
  "title": "An Abyssal Union",
  "summary": "Deep beneath Coruscant, a joint Imperial and Maffi strike team battles through hordes of mutants to reach a vertical tunnel leading to the Abyssal Ruins beneath a New Republic base. The Sith Lord Tyler Damign (Malign), the crimson Twi'lek crimelord Tyy'sun Eson, and stormtroopers Tanis, Cantrell, Siva, Jarek, and the huntress Sidi descend a treacherous 150-foot shaft swarming with biting spiders, losing a Maffi soldier to the beast waiting below. At the cavern floor, a massive horned creature charges; Tyler lures it away into the tunnels while the others scramble to plant demolition charges on the support columns. Man-sized spiders ambush the charge-setters, gravely wounding Tyy'sun with venom and nearly killing Siva before they are slain. With charges set and pheromone decoys deployed to divert the mutants, the battered teams fight their way back up the inclining tunnels toward the surface, Eson masking his poisoning through sheer will as Cantrell calls for a medical team.",
